            "text": "Sophos Home Premium",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " goes far beyond simply preventing known malware and goes further than traditional, signature-based antivirus protection. The product takes a whole new proactive approach by seeking out and analyzing suspicious behaviors and activities using data gathered by the company’s threat intelligence center, Sophos Labs. This helps ensure you’re protected from any new and developing malware, ransomware, exploits, PUAs (Potentially Unwanted Application), phishing attacks, compromised websites, and more.",
